  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The main purpose of this study is to determine whether four weeks treatment with oral
      doxycycline is as effective as three weeks treatment with intravenous ceftriaxone in patients
      with Lyme neuroborreliosis. The other purpose is to improve laboratory diagnostics of Lyme
      neuroborreliosis and further define the manifestations and epidemiology of the disease in
      Finland.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
